long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Do you need to export your Amazon, Walmart, TEMU or eBay Order history to Excel or CSV to efficiently manage and analyze your orders? 

Look no further! Our eCommerce Order History Downloader Chrome extension is designed to streamline your order data and provide you with valuable insights.

Key Features:

üì¶ CSV Order Export: With just a few clicks, export your Amazon, Walmart or eBay orders into a neatly organized CSV file. Keep track of your sales by year, making financial record-keeping a breeze.

üõçÔ∏è Product Grouping: Easily categorize your orders based on the ordered items/products. 

üìä Google Sheets Integration: Take your data analysis to the next level by exporting your Amazon, Walmart or eBay orders and product details directly into Google Sheets. Keep your financial data up to date and accessible from anywhere.

üßæ Organized Reports: Keep your business data organized and accessible. Create separate sheets for orders and product grouping, making it simple to find the information you need.

üîç Product Chart Analysis: Generate a informative graphs that visualizes your order data analysis. Demo https://www.orderproanalytics.com/analytics/demo

Support: 
For any questions, issues, or assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our dedicated support team. We're here to help!
